<font size="3" color="#660099"><b>Vibur DBCP Hibernate 4.0, 4.1, 4.2 Integration</b></font>

Latest version from maven central is [#Maven_dependency_and_how_to_build: 1.0.0]. Here is a link to [https://code.google.com/p/vibur-dbcp-hibernate4/source/browse/CHANGELOG?repo=012 changelog].

This project provides Hibernate 4.0, 4.1, 4.2 integration for [https://code.google.com/p/vibur-dbcp/ Vibur DBCP], a JDBC connection pool.

<br/>
==== Maven dependency and how to build: ====

{{{
<dependency>
  <groupId>org.vibur</groupId>
  <artifactId>vibur-dbcp-hibernate4-012</artifactId>
  <version>1.0.0</version>
</dependency>
}}}

Building the sources is simply a matter of executing:

  `mvn clean install`
